                    <span>I do not write reviews often but I felt compelled to thank Mr. Spoelstra for this fine piece of work.  I believe that this book is especially helpful to small business owners.  It is a great read and it has interactive qualities.  This is a must keep for my bookshelf.</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">Excellent!</div>
